## 1. Project Overview

This PCB is a **signal/power/filtering/connector distribution board**. No motor drivers, no H-bridge ICs on-board. All high-power switching is external.

### System Topology
```
3S Li-ion 18650 ×3 (9V–12.6V, 11.1V nom)
        │
        [F1: 15A Blade Fuse]
        │
        [Q1: IRF9540N TO-220 P-MOSFET — Reverse Polarity Protection]
        │
        ├──→ [XL4016-A external] → 6V/10A → J2 → PCA9685 V+ → MG996R Servos
        ├──→ [XL4016-B external] → 5V/10A → J3 → RPi 5 + ESP32 VIN
        │                                       → AMS1117-3.3 → 3.3V/1A (on PCB)
        └──→ VBAT direct → J9 screw terminals → L298N H-bridge
```

### Power Rails

| Rail | Source | Max Current | Consumers |
|------|--------|-------------|-----------|
| VBAT | 3S Li-ion direct | 15A (fused) | L298N via J9 |
| +6V_SERVO | XL4016-A external | 10A | PCA9685 V+ → 4× MG996R servos |
| +5V | XL4016-B external | 10A | RPi 5 (GPIO pins 2/4), ESP32 VIN |
| +3V3 | AMS1117-3.3 on PCB | 1A | ESP32 VCC, IMU, logic pull-ups |
| GND | Solid plane In1.Cu | — | All returns |

