## 3. Bill of Materials — AS PLACED

### 3.1 Power Input & Protection

| Ref | Qty | Component | Value / Part | Package | Net(s) | Notes |
|-----|-----|-----------|-------------|---------|--------|-------|
| J1 | 1 | 2-pin header | VBAT_IN | 2-pin 5.08mm | VBAT, GND | Battery positive + negative input |
| F1 | 1 | Blade fuse holder | 15A | 2-pin 5.08mm | VBAT, Net-(F1-2) | Main input protection |
| Q1 | 1 | P-Channel MOSFET | IRF9540N | TO-220-3_Vertical | Gate, VBAT_SWITCHED, Net-(Q1-S) | Reverse polarity protection |
| D1 | 1 | TVS Diode | SMBJ12A | D_SMB | GND, VBAT_SWITCHED | Transient suppression on VBAT_SWITCHED |
| R5 | 1 | Resistor | 10kΩ | Axial THT | Net-(Q1-G), VBAT | Gate divider — upper |
| R6 | 1 | Resistor | 10kΩ | Axial THT | Net-(Q1-G), GND | Gate divider — lower |

**Gate Divider (IRF9540N):**
```
Source (VBAT) ──[R5: 10kΩ]──► Gate
                                 │
                            [R6: 10kΩ]
                                 │
                                GND
Vgs = -(VBAT × 0.5)
At 12.6V: Vgs = -6.3V ✅ (IRF9540N threshold: -2V to -4V)
```

